<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>be left in peace • rest in peace</xh5><p> <i>be left in peace—</i>be free from interference or coercion: These men should <u>be left in peace</u> for they have served their time.</p><p> <i>rest in peace</i>—(euph.) said of smb. dead and buried: My grandparents, who now <u>rest in peace</u>, loved Halloween.</p> </entry>
